-- Kumba Wage Offer Rejected by South Africa's National Union of Mineworkers
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-07-15T08:54:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/kumba-wage-offer-rejected-by-south-africa-s-national-union-of-mineworkers.html

          
          
             Kumba Iron Ore Ltd.’s latest pay
offer has been rejected by members of South Africa’s National
Union of Mineworkers, the labor union said in an e-mailed
statement today.  
          
          


  


        